Holly Woodlawn https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Holly_Woodlawn 0 Holly Woodlawn (October 26, 1946 – December 6, 2015) was a transgender Puerto Rican actress and Warhol superstar who appeared in his movies Trash (1970) and Women in Revolt (1971). She was probably best known as the Holly in Lou Reed's hit pop song "Walk on the Wild Side".
